  m_text: "21/08/1997\n\tDidn't expect to get bit. It was a routine scavenge run.\n\tDidn't
    expect I would still be here. John chopped my leg off, saved my life.\n\tDidn't
    expect it would help. But it did. \n\n\tNeed antibiotics to survive, to stave
    off the zombie virus."
